OL,3,CDramatic video shows off duty officers
OL,4,Crush to disarm knife-wielding attacker
OL,6,FA knife-wielding attacker has been
OL,7,Fjailed after a group of off-duty
OL,8,Fofficers rushed to intervene as he
OL,9,Fattacked another man in south London.
OL,11,FPolice rushed to the scene on foot
OL,12,Fwithout any protective equipment, such
OL,13,Fas batons or pepper spray or any
OL,14,Fpolice radios.
OL,16,FThey managed to work together to close
OL,17,Foff the suspect's possible escape
OL,18,Froute and swiftly arrest him.
