OL,3,CDramatic video shows off duty officers
OL,4,Crush to disarm knife-wielding attacker
OL,6,FJoseph Jimenez, 20, was jailed for a
OL,7,Ftotal of eight month at a young
OL,8,Foffenders' institute.
OL,10,FDetective Inspector Jon Summers said:
OL,11,F"The heroism shown by these officers
OL,12,Fis nothing short of exceptional.
OL,14,F"They placed themselves at real risk
OL,15,Fof serious injury in order to prevent
OL,16,Fserious harm and to apprehend an
OL,17,Foffender. It is actions such as these
OL,18,Fthat demonstrate the true heart and
OL,19,Fsoul of the Met.J"They are a credit to
OL,20,Fthemselves, the unit and MPS as a
OL,21,Fwhole."
