OL,3,CDramatic video shows off duty officers
OL,4,Crush to disarm knife-wielding attacker
OL,6,FOn seeing the officers the suspect
OL,7,Fthrew the knife at them and attempted
OL,8,Fto run away but was swiftly arrested.
OL,9,FOfficers carried out first aid to the
OL,10,Fvictim and he was taken to hospital
OL,11,Ffor treatment for a head injury.
OL,13,FThe officers' fast action likely
OL,14,Fprevented him from sustaining any more
OL,15,Fserious injuries.JPolice recovered
OL,16,FCCTV and witness accounts which would
OL,17,Flater leave the suspect with no choice
OL,18,Fbut to plead guilty.JHe was charged on
OL,19,F22 July 2023 and remanded in custody.
