OL,6,FChief Superintendent Seb Adjei-Addoh,
OL,7,Flead for policing in Southwark and
OL,8,FLambeth, added:
OL,10,F"While we expect officers to protect
OL,11,Fthe public, we expect this of them
OL,12,Fwhilst on duty - with proper
OL,13,Fprotective equipment and support.
OL,14,FThese officers had none of this
OL,15,Fequipment and were not aware of
OL,16,Fwhether support was on the way or not.
