OL,3,CDramatic video shows off duty officers
OL,4,Crush to disarm knife-wielding attacker
OL,6,F"They had no way of knowing who had
OL,7,Fweapons or how many. They simply
OL,8,Fresponded to what they could see - had
OL,9,Fthey not acted, a member of the public
OL,10,Fmay have been caused serious or
OL,11,Fpotentially fatal injuries.J"On seeing
OL,12,Fthe spontaneous intervention of the
OL,13,Foff duty officers all other
OL,14,Fprotagonists fled the scene and a
OL,15,Flarge scale public disorder incident
OL,16,Fwas averted.J"We are incredibly proud
OL,17,Fof them."
